   iii. Personal study
This explicitly excludes any use by or within commercial or revenue-generating educational institutions, organizations, or entities.

b. "Commercial/Profit-Making Purposes" means:
   i. Any direct or indirect use of the Software that generates revenue, financial gain, or other commercial benefits
   ii. Any use that promotes or supports revenue-generating activities
   iii. Any use within a commercial organization or entity
   iv. Any use that creates content, services, or products that generate revenue, regardless of whether the Software itself is directly monetized

c. "Non-Commercial Distribution" means the sharing or redistribution of the Software or modifications of the Software where:
   i. No direct monetary compensation, subscription fees, or commercial gain is received
   ii. No indirect monetary benefits are derived (including but not limited to advertising revenue, promotional value, or use in revenue-generating content)
   iii. The distribution is not part of or in support of any commercial activity

d. "Notice" means written communication delivered through one of the following methods:
   i. Email to the licensee's last known email address, with confirmation of receipt
   ii. Certified mail to the licensee's last known physical address
   iii. Direct message to the licensee's registered account on the platform where the Software was obtained
Written confirmation of receipt by the licensee, through any medium, constitutes valid notice.

e. "Substantial Portion" means any amount of the Software's code or documentation that implements or explains any functionality of the Software, regardless of size.


